{"tid":1974242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一套睇幾多次都會喊嘅漫畫：少年犯之七人","createTime":"2020-04-15T16:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T17:01:42.000Z","uid":193209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a800d2fb159fe9ee6dc8f5f2efd41543d9f03dfb","tid":1974242,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"唔知有無同好<br />\n啱啱又重新睇一次，明知劇情係點<br />\n但都忍唔住眼濕濕，套嘢係sell兄弟情<br />\n如果係其他漫畫可以太over，但呢套係講二戰後嘅日本<br />\n啲低下層賤過地底泥，亦係作者自己喺收容所嘅所見所閒/經歴<br />\n例如佢哋幾個合力捱過一關，作者會話佢哋友情勝過一切<br />\n但自己童年時就無咁好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n漫畫最後作者話休息吓會有下一部<br />\n但隔咁多年應該唔會再出了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sLWLJt1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsLWLJt1.png&h=601b6cf0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n櫻哥好錫佢嘅後輩<br />\n現代真實仲有無呢類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137197fbfe9b01a9c1fec161c7799b4e5d6033df","tid":1974242,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"diu開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}